y Zack Snyder. He reprised his role in the prequel film, Army of Thieves, which he also directed.\n\nDescription above from the Wikipedia article Matthias Schweighöfer, licensed under CC-BY-SA, full list of contributors on Wikipedia.","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"DE","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"Matthias Schweighöfer ist ein deutscher Schauspieler und Filmemacher, der für seine Arbeit in mehreren deutschen und amerikanischen Filmproduktionen bekannt ist. Bekannt wurde er durch seine Rolle als Leutnant Franz Herber im Film „Walküre“ aus dem Jahr 2008. 2021 trat Schweighöfer als Ludwig Dieter im Netflix-Film „Army of the Dead“ unter der Regie von Zack Snyder auf. Er wiederholte seine Rolle im Prequel-Film „Army of Thieves“, bei dem er auch Regie führte.","name":"Matthias Schweighöfer","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"CZ","iso_639_1":"cs","name":"Český","english_name":"Czech","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"VN","iso_639_1":"vi","name":"Tiếng Việt","english_name":"Vietnamese","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"JP","iso_639_1":"ja","name":"日本語","english_name":"Japanese","data":{"biography":"","name":"マティアス・シュヴァイクホファー","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"SA","iso_639_1":"ar","name":"العربية","english_name":"Arabic","data":{"biography":"","name":"ماتياس شفيغوفر","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Маттиас Швайгхёфер","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"UA","iso_639_1":"uk","name":"Український","english_name":"Ukrainian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Маттіас Швайґгефер","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"IL","iso_639_1":"he","name":"עִבְרִית","english_name":"Hebrew","data":{"biography":"","name":"מתיאס שווייגהופר","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"마티아스 슈바이크회퍼","primary":false