ame":"Гао Тянь Ни","primary":false}}]}},"person_1582036_translations":{"at":1774377032535,"data":{"id":1582036,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"陳安瑩，香港女演員，配音演員，畢業於聖安當女書院，後為無線電視藝員訓練班第八期藝員，90年代兼任自由身配音演員。\n\nTVB第八期藝員訓練班（1979年）成員，陳安瑩堪稱金庸劇的御用配角。據統計她在TVB共演過8次/位金庸人物，是女星中演金庸劇最多的。其中3次出演傻姑：83版《射鵰》和《神鵰》、還有《九五神鵰俠情侶》。另外還陸續演過殷離、韓小瑩、天山童姥等等。也曾在影集《人鬼狐》中飾演「謝曉彤」《日月神之劍》中飾演「嬌驕女」。如今常在TVB的劇集中擔任小配角。除外亦常為電視台/VCD的劇集/動畫配音。","name":"陳安瑩","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"陈安莹，香港女演员，配音演员，毕业于圣安当女书院，后为无线电视艺员训练班第八期艺员，90年代兼任自由身配音演员。\n\nTVB第八期艺员训练班（1979年）成员，陈安莹堪称金庸剧的御用配角。据统计她在TVB一共演过8次/位金庸人物，是女演员中演金庸剧最多的。其中3次出演傻姑：83版《射雕》和《神雕》、还有《九五神雕侠侣》。此外还陆续演过殷离、韩小莹、天山童姥等等。还在剧集《人鬼狐》中饰演“谢晓彤”《日月神剑》中饰演“娇骄女”。如今经常在TVB的剧集中担任小配角。除外亦经常为电视台/VCD的剧集/动画配音。","name":"陈安莹","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Chan On-ying","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"陳安瑩，香港女演員，配音演員，畢業於聖安當女書院，後為無線電視藝員訓練班第八期藝員，90 年代兼任自由身配音演員。\n\nTVB 第八期藝員訓練班（1979 年）成員，陳安瑩堪稱金庸劇的禦用配角。據統計她在 TVB 共演過 8 次/位金庸人物，是女星中演金庸劇最多的。其中 3 次出演傻姑：83 版《射鵰》和《神鵰》、還有《九五神鵰俠情侶》。另外還陸續演過殷離、韓小瑩、天山童姥等等。也曾在影集《人鬼狐》中飾演「謝曉彤」《日月神之劍》中飾演「嬌驕女」。如今常在 TVB 的劇集中擔任小配角。除外亦常為電視台/VCD 的劇集/動畫配音。","name":"陳安瑩","primary":true}}]}},"person_87583_translations":{"at":1774377040744,"data":{"id":87583,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Chafurin","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"茶风林（日语：茶風林／ちゃふうりん Chafūrin，1961年12月4日—）是日本男性声优。大泽事务所所属。埼玉县出身。以前曾用本名岛泽弘隆（日语：嶋澤 弘隆／しまざわ ひろたか Shimazao Hirotaka）活动，艺名取自卓别林的谐音。东洋大学毕业。","name":"茶风林","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"챠후린","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"JP","iso_639_1":"ja","name":"日本語","english_name":"Japanese","data":{"biography":"旧名：島沢 弘隆（しまざわ ひろたか） 本名：嶋澤 弘隆（読みは同じ）","name":"茶風林","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"DE","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"","name":"Chafurin","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Чафурин","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CZ","iso_639_1":"cs","name":"Český","english_name":"Czech","data":{"biography":"","name":"Čafúrin","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"FR","iso_639_1":"fr","name":"Français","english_name":"French","data":{"biography":"","name":"Chafurin","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"ES","iso_639_1":"es","name":"Español","english_name":"Spanish","data":{"biography":"","name":"Chafurin","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"IT","iso_639_1":"it","name":"Italiano","english_name":"Italian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Chafūrin","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"UA","iso_639_1":"uk","name":"Український","english_name":"Ukrainian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Чяфурін","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"茶風林","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"BR","iso_639_1":"pt","name":"Português","english_name":"Portuguese","data":{"biography":"","name":"Chafurin","primary":false}}]}},"movie_1640489_keywords":{"at":1774377044470,"data":{"id":1640489,"keywords":[]}},"movie_1634301_keywords":{"at":1774377050131,"data":{"id":1634301,"keywords":[]}},"person_1363147_translations":{"at":1774377053983,"data":{"id":1363147,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Oscar Foronda","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"FR","iso_639_1":"fr","name":"Français","english_name":"French","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"MX","iso_639_1":"es","name":"Español","english_name":"Spanish","data":{"biography":"","name":"Oscar Foronda","primary":true}}]}},"person_552067_translations":{"at":1774377058438,"data":{"id":552067,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Kim Tae-hun is a South Korean actor. Kim graduated from Hanyang University, then began his acting career with the Hanyang Repertory Theatre in 1997. Onscreen, he has played leading roles in indie films such as Way to Go, Rose, The Pit and the Pendulum and When Winter Screams.","name":"Kim Tae-hun","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"김태훈","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"金太勋 （김태훈），韩国男演员，1975年5月26日出生于韩国庆尚道大邱，汉阳大学戏剧影视专业毕业。\n\n参演作品有《孤胆特工》、《如果你是我5》、《求婚大作战》等。 亲哥哥是韩国演员金泰佑。2012年在《善良的男人》中饰演坏人律师，2013年在情景剧《一丝的纯情》中饰演男一号郑雨盛。 2015年，金泰勋确认出演JTBC金土电视剧《亲爱的恩东啊》，饰演崔在浩。 同年，客串出演tvN金土连续剧《请回答1988》，饰演一名医生。 2017年5月，出演MBC月火剧《守望者》，饰演一名检察官。","name":"金太勋","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"金太勳","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"FR","iso_639_1":"fr","name":"Français","english_name":"French","data":{"biography":"Kim Tae-hoon est un acteur sud-coréen. Kim est diplômé de l'Université de Hanyang, puis a commencé sa carrière d'acteur au Hanyang Repertory Theatre en 1997. À l'écran, il a joué des rôles principaux dans des films indépendants tels que Way to Go, Rose, The Pit and the Pendulum et When Winter Screams. Wikipedia","name":"Kim Tae-hoon","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"DE","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"金太勳 （김태훈），韓國男演員，1975 年 5 月 26 日出生於韓國慶尚道大邱，漢陽大學戲劇影視專業畢業。\n\n參演作品有《殺手代父》、《如果你是我 5》、《求婚大作戰》等。\n\n親哥哥是韓國演員金泰佑。2012 年在《善良的男人》中飾演壞人律師，2013 年在情景劇《一絲的純情》中飾演男一號鄭雨盛。\n\n2015 年，金泰勳確認出演 JTBC 金土電視劇《親愛的恩東啊》，飾演崔在浩。\n\n同年，客串出演 tvN 金土聯續劇《請回答 1988》，飾演一名醫生。\n\n2017 年 5 月，出演 MBC 月火劇《保衞奇俠》，飾演一名檢察官。","name":"金太勳","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"SK","iso_639_1":"sk","name":"Slovenčina","english_name":"Slovak","data":{"biography":"","name":"Kim Tae-hun","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"ES","iso_639_1":"es","name":"Español","english_name":"Spanish","data":{"biography":"Kim Tae-hun (coreano: 김태훈) es un actor surcoreano nacido el 26 de mayo de 1975 en Seúl, Corea del Sur. Está representado por la agencia L'July Entertainment.\n\nEstudió Teatro y Cine en la Hanyang University, donde se formó como actor. Comenzó su carrera en 1997 cuando se unió al grupo teatral de su universidad, el Hanyang Repertory Theatre. A partir de ahí desarrolló una trayectoria profesional en cine, teatro y televisión que se extiende hasta la actualidad. A lo largo de los años ha participado en películas independientes y comerciales, así como en series de televisión populares. Entre sus trabajos destacados en cine figuran películas como «Way to Go, Rose» (2006), «The Pit and the Pendulum» (2009) y «When Winter Screams» (2013). En televisión, ha intervenido en producciones como «The Man from Nowhere» (2010), «You're So Pretty» (2011), «The Innocent Man» (2012), «An Ethics Lesson» (2013) o «Pure Love» (2013), entre otras. Además de su trayectoria en cine y televisión, Kim Tae-hun tiene un hermano mayor también actor, Kim Tae-woo.","name":"Kim Tae-hun","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Ким Тхэ Хун","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"JP","iso_639_1":"ja","name":"日本語","english_name":"Japanese","data":{"biography":"","name":"キム・テフン","primary":false}}]}},"person_1817976_translations":{"at":1774377061104,"data":{"id":1817976,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"DE","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","da