d":1566818,"known_for_department":"Directing","name":"Mohamed Ben Attia","original_name":"Mohamed Ben Attia","popularity":0.749,"profile_path":"/6Pdf9SE1FIMkZaqvV3TRNk7Aa56.jpg","credit_id":"63f5cfaffc31d300a1317448","department":"Directing","job":"Director"},{"adult":false,"gender":2,"id":1566818,"known_for_department":"Directing","name":"Mohamed Ben Attia","original_name":"Mohamed Ben Attia","popularity":0.749,"profile_path":"/6Pdf9SE1FIMkZaqvV3TRNk7Aa56.jpg","credit_id":"63f5cfb37dfda60085ac5ba8","department":"Writing","job":"Writer"}]}},"person_3186832_translations":{"at":1774377094008,"data":{"id":3186832,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Chelsea von Holst","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CH","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"","name":"Chelsea von Holst","primary":true}}]}},"person_75913_translations":{"at":1774377094668,"data":{"id":75913,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Ha Jung-woo (Korean: 하정우; born Kim Sung-hoon on March 11, 1978) is a South Korean actor, film director, screenwriter and film producer. One of the highest grossing actors in South Korea, Ha's starring films have accumulated more than 100 million tickets. Only 3 other actors have reached this milestone, with Ha being nearly a decade younger than the rest when achieving this.\n\nHis breakthrough to stardom came with the role in Na Hong-jin's serial killer film The Chaser (2008). One of the leading actors of his generation in Korean cinema, Ha showcased his versatility across films of various genres: road movie My Dear Enemy (2008), sports film Take Off (2009), action thriller The Yellow Sea (2010), gangster saga Nameless Gangster: Rules of the Time (2012), romantic comedy Love Fiction (2012), spy actioner The Berlin File (2013), and action thriller The Terror Live (2013). Ha is also known for his role as grim reaper Gang-rim in the fantasy action film Along with the Gods: The Two Worlds (2017) and its 2018 sequel.\n\nHe made his directorial debut through the comedy film Fasten Your Seatbelt (2013), followed by Chronicle of a Blood Merchant (2015).","name":"Ha Jung-woo","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"하정우","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"河正宇（하정우、Ha Jung Woo），1978年3月11日出生于韩国，毕业于韩国中央大学，韩国男演员。\n\n2002年，拍摄剧情片《认真生活》从而出道。\n\n2005年，凭借剧情片《不可饶恕》获得第25届韩国影评奖最佳男新人奖。\n\n2006年，主演剧情片《时间》。\n\n2008年，主演惊悚片《追击者》，凭借该片获得第11届亚洲影评人协会奖最佳男主角和第16届春史电影节最佳男演员奖。\n\n2009年，凭借动作片《国家代表》获得第46届百想艺术大赏电影部门最佳男演员奖。\n\n2010年，主演由罗宏镇执导的动作片《黄海》，凭借该片获得第47届百想艺术大赏电影部门最佳男演员奖。\n\n2013年，主演动作片《柏林》，凭借该片获得第49届百想艺术大赏电影部门最佳男演员奖。\n\n2015年，凭借动作片《暗杀》获得第52届韩国电影大钟奖最佳男演员奖提名。\n\n2016年，主演灾难片《隧道》和悬疑片《小姐》。\n\n2017年，主演动作片《绝地隧战》。\n\n2018年，主演奇幻片《与神同行》系列电影。\n\n2019年，主演灾难片《白头山》。\n\n2020年，主演悬疑恐怖片《衣橱》。","name":"河正宇","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"河正宇","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"PT","iso_639_1":"pt","name":"Português","english_name":"Portuguese","data":{"biography":"","name":"Ha Jeong-woo","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Ха Чон У","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"FR","iso_639_1":"fr","name":"Français","english_name":"French","data":{"biography":"","name":"Ha Jeong-Woo","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"河正宇（하정우、Ha Jung Woo），1978 年 3 月 11 日出生於韓國，畢業於韓國中央大學，韓國男演員。\n\n2002 年，拍攝劇情片《認真生活》從而出道。\n\n2005 年，憑藉劇情片《豪情蓋天》獲得第 25 屆韓國影評獎最佳男新人獎。\n\n2006 年，主演劇情片《慾望的謊容》。\n\n2008 年，主演驚悚片《追擊者》，憑藉該片獲得第 11 屆亞洲影評人協會獎最佳男主角和第 16 屆春史電影節最佳男演員獎。\n\n2009 年，憑藉動作片《國家代表》獲得第 46 屆百想藝術大賞電影部門最佳男演員獎。\n\n2010 年，主演由羅宏鎮執導的動作片《追擊者 2 之黃海殺機》，憑藉該片獲得第 47 屆百想藝術大賞電影部門最佳男演員獎。\n\n2013 年，主演動作片《柏林》，憑藉該片獲得第 49 屆百想藝術大賞電影部門最佳男演員獎。\n\n2015 年，憑藉動作片《復國者聯盟》獲得第 52 屆韓國電影大鐘獎最佳男演員獎提名。\n\n2016 年，主演災難片《血隧》和懸疑片《下女誘罪》。\n\n2017 年，主演動作片《轟天暴隊》。\n\n2018 年，主演奇幻片《與神同行》系列電影。\n\n2019 年，主演災難片《白頭山：火山浩劫》。\n\n2020 年，主演懸疑恐怖片《兇櫃》。","name":"河正宇","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"IT","iso_639_1":"it","name":"Italiano","english_name":"Italian","data":{"biography":"Ha Jung-woo è un attore, regista, sceneggiatore e produttore cinematografico sudcoreano. Uno degli attori con i maggiori incassi in Corea del Sud, i film da lui interpretati hanno totalizzato oltre 100 milioni di biglietti incassati. Solo altri tre attori hanno raggiunto questo traguardo.","name":"Ha Jung-woo","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"UA","iso_639_1":"uk","name":"Український","english_name":"Ukrainian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Ха Чон У","primary":false}}]}},"person_6070615_translations":{"at":1774377095208,"data":{"id":6070615,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Chu Aixu","primary":false}}]}},"person_36554_translations":{"at":1774377115511,"data":{"id":36554,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Mary Beth Peil is an American singer, stage and screen actress, best known for her television roles as Evelyn 'Grams' Ryan on \"Dawson's Creek\" and as Jackie Florrick on \"The Good Wife\".","name":"Mary Beth Peil","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"DE","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"玛丽·贝丝·佩尔 （Mary Beth Peil） 是一位美国歌手、舞台和银幕女演员，以在《道森溪》中饰演伊芙琳·瑞恩和在《好妻子》中饰演杰基·弗洛里克而闻名。","name":"玛丽·贝丝·佩尔","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Мэри Бет Пейл","